<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet/less" href="./css/service-process.less" />
    <script src="./config/dots_sum.js"></script>
    <script src="./config/head_import.js"></script>
    <title>服务流程</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="common-head"></div>
	<div id="common-qr"></div>
    <div class="page-service">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="index-t">
                <div>服务流程</div>
                <div>Service process</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-list">
                <div class="service-one d-flex align-items-end">
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">01</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">电话来访</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            电话或来访赛图咨询相关留学问题，确定留学计划。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-img">
                        <img src="./img/service/s1.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex align-items-end">
                    <div class="service-img d-flex justify-content-end">
                        <img src="./img/service/s2.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">02</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">签订协议</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            根据酷虎背景情况，确定服务难点和重点，制定基本留学计划。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex align-items-end">
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">03</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">项目启动</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            专业申请方向利弊分析，专业方向学校申请信息数据分析、对比、评估，选校方向的确定
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-img img3">
                        <img src="./img/service/s3.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex align-items-end">
                    <div class="service-img">
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">04</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">申请实施</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            对专业及其选校方案分析，整理背景素材并设计文书结构规划，挖掘学生亮点，用于essay写作，对文书进行研讨、修改申请表、推荐信、申请费、成绩寄送等申请环节辅助工作。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex">
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">05</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">录取安排</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            根据学校录取通知信息，进行外语课程学习安排。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-img img3">
                        <img src="./img/service/s4.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex">
                    <div class="service-img d-flex justify-content-end">
                        <img src="./img/service/s5.png" alt="" class="img4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">06</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">办理签证</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            合理规划签证及其核心问题回答方式，保证客户签证一次性通过。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex">
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">07</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">行前准备</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            对录取学生分批次进行行前准备指导，并发放赛图独家《美国留学行前知道完全手册》。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-img img3">
                        <img src="./img/service/s6.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-one d-flex">
                    <div class="service-img d-flex justify-content-end">
                        <img src="./img/service/s7.png" alt="" class="img4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-left">
                        <div class="left-top d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="top-one flex-shrink-0">08</div>
                            <div class="top-two flex-shrink-1">后续服务</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="left-bottom">
                            跟踪学生入学、注册、缴费事宜，并定期安排赛图海外办公室人员奔赴各个院校探望赛图学子。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="common-footer"></div>
    <script src="./config/body_import.js"></script>
</body>

</html>